Body: Description: Published Reports do not open.
What We've Learned Updated: EMEA Customer
Next Steps Updated: Close the case as issue has been resolved.

What We've Learned Updated: The customer has recently upgraded NEA. It appears that the account used to Access NEA didn't had permissions on SQL server. This KB article was shared with customer after initial probing:

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000Qs9KAE.html

Steps to Reproduce Updated: The account used to run the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Web Server service does not have access to the Enterprise Auditor database.
